{
  "stem": "10768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had, at that time, a very big clinic, which was on a pretty high level, considering-- I am comparing to the size of our town from until the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was in the clinic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She had a very good education from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was married to a-- her husband was born in our town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he had parents in our town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because of that, they were running from Krakow, and they remain in our town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At the same time-- this friend's name was Irene-- and her mother and three sisters also came from near Krakow, from a town village, God, they were-- everybody was running.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When they came to Lesko, since she was in Lesko and she was the head nurse, they also stayed there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now this, I'm going back to about the, the time of 1940, I would say April 1940.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "At that time, since our town was on the boundary, the Russians felt that the element which ran from the Germans-- a lot of them left family behind there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And at one time, they said that people who want to go back to their previous homes, on the German territory, they could register.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there's going to be an exchange of some Volksdeutsche from Russians-- anyhow, there was going to be an exchange between the Germans and the Russians.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I don't know if this was a trick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Or perhaps there was an exchange.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But the people who registered to go back to their home was 10 or 20 times bigger than the ones, perhaps, from the German territory to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one night, in April, approximately April 1940, in the middle of the night, at 12 o'clock-- and this was exactly, I would say, the methods of the Germans-- the Russians had this order.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
